cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as pose estimation and video retargeting, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The use of a generative model and meta-learning techniques suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also deals with adapting to different backgrounds, which could fall under cs.GR. Finally, the use of videos and images suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.MM.
